data.description: - Welcome to 15 South Way in the quaint village of Walden, where you will find this lovingly maintained home. Tastefully upgraded including new stainless steal appliances, an open concept kitchen/dining area with tile floors. Generously sized 3 bedrooms with ample closet space and a beautifully updated bathroom. The lower level offers a cozy, comfortable and spacious family room, a second full bathroom and walkout to a brand new deck. Sit and relax on the rear two tiered deck, with plenty of space for outdoor gatherings, overlooking your private backyard. A 1 car garage and and large driveway with ample parking is ideal for entertaining or parking your RV and/or boat. An added bonus is the combination shed/storage, fully wired with electricity. A must see, so schedule today before it goes!
